- What do I say?

02:23.449 --> 02:26.418
"Hello, biological Mom Hope.

02:26.452 --> 02:29.086
- My name is Maura. I didn't die at birth."
- Shut up.

02:29.121 --> 02:30.722
No, you shouldn't say, "shut up."

02:30.756 --> 02:32.456
Dr. Isles.

02:32.491 --> 02:35.360
Oh, hello, Dr. Martin.
What a surprise.

02:38.665 --> 02:41.367
Oh, yes, I-I would love
to have dinner with you.

02:41.401 --> 02:44.370
Tonight would be great.

02:44.404 --> 02:46.572
Uh, would you like to
come over to my house?

02:46.607 --> 02:48.641
Sure, you ...
you can bring your daughter.

02:48.676 --> 02:51.177
Okay, I ...
I will text you my address.

02:51.211 --> 02:54.780
I-I look forward to it.
Okay, bye-bye.

02:54.815 --> 02:57.517
Oh, my gosh.

02:57.551 --> 02:59.252
Why did I invite them here?
The place is a wreck.

02:59.286 --> 03:01.521
Oh, I'd be so embarrassed

03:01.555 --> 03:04.324
- to invite anyone but me here.
- And what will I serve?

03:04.358 --> 03:08.361
I mean, she probably has a more refined
palate than me.

03:08.395 --> 03:11.364
Oh, saved by murder. Come on.

03:11.398 --> 03:13.766
No, no, I-I can't go.
I have way too much to do.

03:13.801 --> 03:16.503
Okay, I think I can
do an autopsy by now.

03:16.537 --> 03:18.271
Well, I to take have a shower.

03:18.305 --> 03:19.806
Maura.

03:19.840 --> 03:21.741
