12:04.069 --> 12:09.106
he ... he had financial issues,
so I always had to work.

12:09.140 --> 12:12.209
- That's hard.
- Look, Cailin's back.

12:12.243 --> 12:14.878
I think I'll use your ladies' room, too.

12:14.912 --> 12:16.379
Ah, good idea.

12:22.285 --> 12:23.985
Cailin hates me.

12:24.020 --> 12:26.721
She's 18.

12:26.755 --> 12:30.924
She hates everybody over 18...
and under 18.

12:30.959 --> 12:32.259
She's my sister, Jane.

12:32.294 --> 12:34.195
Even when they know
they're related to you,

12:34.229 --> 12:35.863
families are still complicated.

12:48.313 --> 12:54.185
- Hey. This is pretty good.
- Oh, no, thank you.

12:54.219 --> 12:57.088
Really? Not even one bite?

13:08.267 --> 13:10.369
What are you listening to?

13:10.403 --> 13:13.072
Oh. Music.

13:13.106 --> 13:15.372
What kind of bands do you like?

13:17.041 --> 13:22.444
It was nice of you to bring
the cake over. But it's okay.

13:22.479 --> 13:24.680
You don't have to try to engage with me.

13:24.714 --> 13:25.747
Are we that awful?

13:28.183 --> 13:30.785
Will you tell my Mom
that I decided to walk home?

13:30.819 --> 13:32.820
Wait, what?

13:32.854 --> 13:35.689
It's not personal.
I just would like to be alone.

13:44.332 --> 13:48.101
- Was that Cailin?
- She said she wanted to be alone.

13:48.135 --> 13:52.839
Did Cailin leave?
Are you leaving?

13:52.873 --> 13:57.010
She's very fragile right now.
Thank you for dinner. I'm so sorry.

14:02.316 --> 14:04.819
What the hell just happened?

14:12.062 --> 14:16.466
I don't think Cailin should have
been forced to have dinner with us. 

14:16.534 --> 14:18.535
Why weren't you this
evolved when I was 18?

14:21.572 --> 14:23.807
Smells so good.

14:24.341 --> 14:26.910
I'm so sorry about last night.

14:26.944 --> 14:30.080
