service to keep food warm.

34:44.329 --> 34:45.763
The caterers.

34:45.797 --> 34:48.199
That's why we couldn't match
the hair to a call girl.

34:48.233 --> 34:49.867
It's got to be from a caterer waiter.

34:49.902 --> 34:54.371
- There's a print here.
- Could be the victim's.

34:54.406 --> 34:58.275
I think a second person tried this
ring on. It's a different print.

35:04.825 --> 35:09.381
So, as financial chair, I want to assure you
your investments are healthy. 

35:09.415 --> 35:12.017
I recommend that we stay the
course with Murray & Bowman.

35:12.052 --> 35:14.386
We recommend you get
a new financial chair.

35:14.454 --> 35:15.654
Excuse me?

35:15.689 --> 35:17.790
You're under arrest for embezzling
your fellow teachers' pension money.

35:19.626 --> 35:22.295
What?
What did you do, Doug?

35:22.329 --> 35:24.864
Spent a bunch of money
on this diamond ring.

35:24.898 --> 35:27.299
Mm. Lucky you, Mrs. Gatz.

35:27.334 --> 35:29.936
Oh, wait.
That was for Georgette, wasn't it?

35:29.970 --> 35:31.771
I don't know what you're talking about.

35:31.805 --> 35:34.341
We found your prints on the ring.
We found Georgette's, too.

35:34.375 --> 35:35.909
You tried it on before you killed her.

35:35.944 --> 35:38.546
- Oh, god.
- We're thinking there was some pillow talk.

35:38.580 --> 35:40.081
You told Lori about
Neal's heart condition,

35:40.115 --> 35:42.083
his trouble getting it
up without an injection.

35:42.118 --> 35:45.453
Handy that you're a nurse, Lori.
Pretty, too.

35:45.488 --> 35:48.023
You snuck in with the catering,
and then you injected potassium chloride

35:48.058 --> 35:49.558
into the man who ruined your life.

35:49.593 --> 35:51.727
Did you know
Doug was having an affair?

35:51.761 --> 35:53.662
Or did you figure it out
after you killed Neal?

35:53.696 --> 35:55.464
This is insane.

35:55.498 --> 35:57.967
Yeah, that's what we
thought when we saw you push

35:57.968 --> 36:00.436
Georgette into the pool
on this surveillance tape.

36:00.470 --> 36:01.870
This is your fault.

36:01.905 --> 36:05.474
<i>- We don't have a surveillance tape.
- She doesn't know that.</i>

36:05.509 --> 36:07.343
You couldn't let go of
your high-school buddies.

36:07.378 --> 36:10.614
We were happy.
But you let Neal drag you in,

36:10.648 --> 36:12.349
show you this life you
thought you were missing.

36:12.383 --> 36:14.885
You fell in love with a whore.

36:14.919 --> 36:18.089
- Let's go, Lori.
- Hands behind your back.

36:24.963 --> 36:28.966
Cailin. Hi.
Come in.

36:31.036 --> 36:35.606
Do you know at the name "Cailin" means?

36:35.640 --> 36:38.910
- No.
- It means "uncertain."

36:38.944 --> 36:41.413
That's the name that
my mother picked for me.

36:41.447 --> 36:45.883
- "Maura" means "great."
- Yes, I know.

36:45.918 --> 36:50.922
- That's the name she picked for you.
- Cailin, please let me explain.

36:50.956 --> 36:52.590
Hmm.

36:52.624 --> 36:54.825
Can you explain why you called
my mother out of the blue

36:54.859 --> 36:57.760
with some bullshit story?

36:57.795 --> 37:00.163
This is very complicated.

37:00.197 --> 37:02.599
She's trying to bond with
me now, since I'm dying.

37:02.633 --> 37:05.802
You know, make up for all
those years she wasn't there.

37:05.836 --> 37:07.137
You're not going to die.

37:07.171 --> 37:11.141
"Don't ... don't do what I did, Cailin."

37:11.175 --> 37:12.876
Right.

37:12.911 --> 37:17.448
Like I'm gonna have time to...
fall in love...

37:18.851 --> 37:22.586
get pregnant...
have a baby...

37:24.522 --> 37:27.157
...hold that baby once
before she dies.

37:29.460 --> 37:33.029
You, um...
you put it back up.

37:34.866 --> 37:38.869
I went snooping.
I found it in the bathroom.

37:38.903 --> 37:42.439
I mean, it is my mother, isn't it?

37:42.474 --> 37:45.709
And that's ...
that's your gravestone...

37:45.743 --> 37:50.213
which is weird because...
you look okay to me.

37:50.248 --> 37:53.083
Please just let me explain.
I didn't mean for any of this to ...

37:53.117 --> 37:55.685
Do you have any idea what it's like

37:55.719 --> 37:58.521
to grow up in the
shadow of a dead baby?!

37:59.957 --> 38:02.559
I was never enough!

38:02.593 --> 38:06.829
You are more than enough.
She loves you.

38:06.864 --> 38:08.964
I know you think
I should have told her ...

38:08.999 --> 38:12.200
- I should have told the both of you, but I ...
- Yeah. Yeah.

38:12.235 --> 38:16.905
- I want to help you.
- I don't want your help!

38:18.575 --> 38:20.743
And I don't want your kidney, either.

38:23.046 --> 38:25.014
Yeah.

38:25.048 --> 38:29.652
Yeah, I...
I thought that was you.

38:32.556 --> 38:37.894
You just... you don't get
a match like that from a stranger.

38:37.928 --> 38:39.895
Cailin, please, don't throw your life away

38:39.930 --> 38:41.930
because of what you think of me.

38:43.666 --> 38:49.038
I don't want any part of you
living in me.

38:50.207 --> 38:54.178
Cailin!
What is going on?

38:54.213 --> 38:57.582
- You followed me?
- Well, you took our car.

38:57.617 --> 38:59.651
- So you called the police?
- Well...

39:01.554 --> 39:05.958
Hope... there's something
I need to tell you.

39:10.094 --> 39:12.229
I'm Paddy Doyle's daughter.

39:15.833 --> 39:16.967
What?

39:18.703 --> 39:20.103
I'm your daughter.

39:23.007 --> 39:25.209
I know that must be strange to hear.

39:25.243 --> 39:26.577
Don't say that.

39:27.713 --> 39:29.280
This is my daughter.

39:29.314 --> 39:32.016
Paddy told you that I died at birth.

39:32.050 --> 39:35.286
I am not looking
to be your daughter.

39:35.320 --> 39:37.288
I ...
I have a mother and a father.

39:37.322 --> 39:39.990
- I just wanted you to know...
- Just stop!

39:40.025 --> 39:41.625
I don't know who you
are or what you want,

39:41.660 --> 39:44.628
but I've had just about
as much as I can bear.

39:44.663 --> 39:50.101
Cailin. Honey.
Let's just go.

40:01.948 --> 40:03.916
I don't know what to say.

40:07.354 --> 40:13.926
Out of all the scenarios I thought of...
that wasn't one of them.

40:18.232 --> 40:22.602
She's in denial.
She's in shock.

40:22.637 --> 40:24.137
Imagine, how would you react

40:24.172 --> 40:26.606
if a grown woman walked
up to you and said...

40:26.640 --> 40:30.277
"How you doing?
I'm your... dead baby."

40:33.048 --> 40:34.615
And what about Cailin?

40:34.649 --> 40:37.285
If she doesn't let me
help her, she'll die.

40:37.319 --> 40:41.756
Maura, you can't force your kidney on her.

40:41.790 --> 40:45.660
I wish I could.

40:47.063 --> 40:52.334
I don't know. I never, ever
meant to cause them any pain.

40:52.368 --> 40:54.369
It's just so awful.

40:55.906 --> 40:58.407
Well, I tried to warn you.

40:58.442 --> 41:02.078
Family sucks.
Blow.

41:04.215 --> 41:05.348
No.

41:06.817 --> 41:09.786
No.
I'm all cried out. Okay?

41:09.821 --> 41:12.790
I'm done.

41:12.824 --> 41:16.193
I'm done.
And, actually, I'm a little insulted.

41:16.227 --> 41:21.432
- What'd I do?
- That girl rejected my kidney.

41:22.701 --> 41:23.801
The nerve.

41:23.836 --> 41:28.006
I know.
Right? It's a very nice kidney.

41:28.041 --> 41:29.742
I'm sure it is.

41:31.078 --> 41:34.013
You should keep it...
in your body.

41:35.282 --> 41:38.318
I'm just saying.

